*** <2025-02-16 Sun>

rough outline of a plan

- compiler
  - reads a file into s-expr
  - s-expr -> module graph
    - imports/exports
    - local definitions
      - s-expr
      - bytecode
    macro expansion phasing comes into play here, not sure how yet
  - local definitions compiled to bytecode
    - macro expansion
    - cps transform
    - optimizations
      - beta reduction
      - constants and simple math
      - others ???
    - ??? -> bytecode
